My best memory with mom is wrap bak chang. Every year during Duanwu Festival, mom always make her own bak chang with the whole family to give away to our relatives and neighbors. I really enjoy so much wrapping the different types of bak chang, got white and black glutinous rice and lots of delicious ingredients. We always have so much fun where my sisters and I will make some special ones for ourselves. Ours are always super big with full of our favorite ingredients inside them till after boiling, the whole lot of ingredients burst out. I’m looking forward to wrap bak chang again with my mom but even after she recovered from a stroke, she doesn’t have the strength to do it again. 
@christinele_life
